# Doctores API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@authToken = {{authToken}}

## Rutas publicas

### Crear doctor (publico)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctores/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docType": "CC",
  "docNumber": "1029860270",
  "name": "Jesus Monsalvo",
  "specialty": "Cardiologia",
  "medicalLicense": "MED-12345",
  "phone": "3001234567",
  "email": "jesus.monsalvo@example.com",
  "user_id": 1,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar doctores (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/doctores/public
Accept: application/json

### Obtener doctor por id (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1/public
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar doctor (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "3209876543",
  "specialty": "Medicina interna",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar doctor fisicamente (publico)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1/public

### Baja logica de doctor (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1/logic/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

## Rutas protegidas (requieren token)

### Crear doctor (con auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docType": "CC",
  "docNumber": "1034567890",
  "name": "Ana Quintero",
  "specialty": "Pediatria",
  "medicalLicense": "MED-67890",
  "phone": "3015554444",
  "email": "ana.quintero@example.com",
  "user_id": 2,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar doctores (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/doctores
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Obtener doctor por id (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar doctor (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "3220001111",
  "specialty": "Dermatologia",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar doctor fisicamente (con auth)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Baja logica de doctor (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/doctor/1/logic
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}
